            <div class="main-content">
                <!-- Intro Section -->
                <div class="intro-section">
                    <p>Whether you're moving for a new job, starting a family, or downsizing for retirement, our professional residential moving services make all the difference. As trusted local movers in Chicago, we offer a comprehensive relocation experience that covers everything you need to settle comfortably into your new home. Our team handles local household moves within the city and cross country relocations with the same level of expertise and dependability.</p>
                </div>

                <!-- Full Service Section -->
                <section>
                    <h2>Full-Service Residential Movers in Chicago, IL</h2>
                    <p>Since 2009 we've helped thousands of tenants and homeowners with relocations to new apartments, condos, townhomes and houses. Our proven approach combines affordable pricing with the reliable service needed to make moving day smooth and stress-free. From creating a custom moving plan to unpacking the final box, we work quickly and diligently without cutting corners.</p>
                    <p>At New City Moving, we take care of every aspect of a residential move. Our movers arrive on time and pack, load and transport items with the care and efficiency your belongings deserve. We also take extra steps to protect your home during the process, preventing scuffs, scratches and marks that could damage walls, floors and doorways.</p>
                </section>

                <!-- Features Grid -->
                <div class="features-grid">
                    <div class="feature-box">
                        <div class="feature-icon">🏠</div>
                        <h4>Expert Local Moving</h4>
                        <p>Specialized in Chicago area moves with knowledge of every neighborhood and building requirement.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feature-box">
                        <div class="feature-icon">🚚</div>
                        <h4>Long Distance Moves</h4>
                        <p>Cross-country relocations handled with professional care and tracking throughout the journey.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feature-box">
                        <div class="feature-icon">📦</div>
                        <h4>Professional Packing</h4>
                        <p>High-quality materials and expert techniques to protect your valuable belongings.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="feature-box">
                        <div class="feature-icon">🛡️</div>
                        <h4>Home Protection</h4>
                        <p>Extra care to prevent damage to walls, floors, and doorways during the move.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Packing and Storage Section -->
                <section>
                    <h2>Packing and Storage for Residential Moves</h2>
                    <p>With extensive experience in moving, our team has refined the packing and unpacking process. Our secure packing services protect items regardless of how far they need to travel. Here's what to expect from the residential packing process:</p>
                    
                    <div class="packing-list">
                        <ul>
                            <li>High-quality packing supplies for household items</li>
                            <li>Protects valuables for long-distance transport</li>
                            <li>Convenient packing for families and professionals</li>
                            <li>Full or partial packing offers flexibility for residential moving</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                    <p>Along with professional packing, we offer safe and flexible storage solutions for times when your new home isn't quite ready or is undergoing renovations. We'll securely store your belongings for as long as needed, then deliver them to your new residence at a time that suits your schedule.</p>
                </section>

                <!-- FAQ Section -->
                <section class="faq-section">
                    <h2>Common Questions About Residential Movers</h2>
                    
                    <div class="faq-item">
                        <div class="faq-question">
                            <span>How long does a residential move usually take?</span>
                            <span class="faq-toggle">+</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="faq-answer">
                            <div class="faq-answer-content">
                                The time it takes for a residential move depends on the number of possessions and the distance to the location. Most local moves, such as those involving a single-family house, are completed in a single day. Long-distance moves typically take one to three days, depending on distance, route and logistics.
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="faq-item">
                        <div class="faq-question">
                            <span>Can residential movers safely handle fragile items?</span>
                            <span class="faq-toggle">+</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="faq-answer">
                            <div class="faq-answer-content">
                                Residential movers can safely handle fragile items using skilled packing methods and heavy-duty packing materials, along with professional equipment and proper loading techniques. Moving items such as art, antiques, glassware and jewelry often involve custom crating, bubble wrap, and padded moving blankets for maximum protection.
                            </div>
